        .d-flex.mt-10.mb-4.align-items-center
            img.me-4(src='assets/img/icons/spinners.svg', alt='...', style='height: 48px;')
            h1.page-header.mb-0 Spinners
        .row.gx-5
            .col-lg-9
                p Spinner indicators express an unspecified wait time or display the length of a process.

                //- Divider
                hr.my-5

                //- * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
